    "description": {
      "value": "<p>As a bonus action, you close your eyes and concentrate on your breathing to cleanse yourself of impurities.</p><p> When you possess any ranks of a condition that you did not inflict on yourself as a result of a feature or jutsu, you remove one of these conditions from yourself.</p><p> This style is even able to clear up your chakra network, regaining you the ability to use features and jutsu with the CM component.</p><p> You may use this style once per short rest.</p><p></p>",
